Package: DiffCircaPipeline
Version: 0.99.0
Title: An R package for DiffCircaPipeline: A framework for multifaceted characterization of differential rhythmicity
Description: The package facilitates a comprehensive and interactive pipeline to capture the multifaceted characteristics of differentially rhythmic biomarkers. It implements rhythmicity detection, differential rhythm parameter test, and differential rhythmicity fitness test. Intensive visualization tools are also provided to help exploration of the data. 
